summary: Just a tweaked version of a CBBE HourGlass model
descriptionHtml:
Nothing fancy to see here. Just a Body Slide preset that I created based on CBBE Hour Glass figure. I like my heroines to be of a Thicc variety so if you like what I like...then enjoy!
